name: WestJet 737-8CT [C-GWSV] "Frozen Livery" Photo Shoot at Calgary Airport ᴴᴰ
description:
On October 18th, WestJet unveiled this new special livery on one of their many 737-800s from Disney's "Frozen", after having been flown to Toronto under the cover of darkness. The following day it flew Toronto-Orlando and back, and then repositioned to YYC late in the evening for this photo shoot with Wolfe Air's Learjet 25B. Includes the taxi, takeoff, and touch and go with ATC throughout, hope you enjoy.

Thanks for watching!
